		<h1 class="header-s">At the Intersection:<br />
Equal Opportunity for All</h1>
		<span class="subtitle">
			Fifty years after the March on Washington, Alexis McGill Johnson reflects on the continued fight for equality and access		</span>
	</div><!-- /section-heading-subtitle -->
</div><!-- main heading -->
<div class="left-col">
	
		<div class="author-image">
